<a href="http://goo.gl/maps/MH9b3">http://goo.gl/maps/MH9b3</a></p>
<p>2-3-36 Koujimachi, Koujimachi Suzuki Bldg Chiyoda-ku, Tokyo
tel: 03-3239-4988</p>
